1. Use a strip of pressure sensitive tape (3M 500 for instance) and apply it firmly on the area to be tested: artwork, logo, marking;
2. Press it on the surface so that the tape is properly stuck, with no bubble or wrinkle; 
3. Remove the tape with an angle close to 180 degrees, rapidly but not jerked.
4. Repeat this operation 3 times.

